    <title>Manjaro</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2023/02/16/manjaro/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2023/02/16/manjaro/</id>
    <published>2023-02-16T03:52:01.642Z</published>
    <updated>2023-02-14T02:55:22.750Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用ventory安装后,开始配置</p><p>原则:开发环境与系统隔离，系统保持最简单安装（KISS原则的一个解释）</p><h2 id="源设置"><a href="#源设置" class="headerlink" title="源设置"></a>源设置</h2><p>官方源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>archlinuxcn镜像源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># /etc/pacman.conf</span><br>[archlinuxcn]<br>Server = https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/<span class="hljs-variable">$arch</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>刷新数据库</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacman -Syy<br>pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Note:该源对应Manjaro unstable分支，注意兼容问题</p><h2 id="区域设置"><a href="#区域设置" class="headerlink" title="区域设置"></a>区域设置</h2><p>Gnome与ibus适配</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacman -S manjaro-asian-input-support-ibus ibus-libpinyin<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>KDE与fcitx5适配</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacman -S manjaro-asian-input-support-fcitx5<br>pacman -S fcitx5-chinese-addons<br>pacman -S fcitx5-material-color<br>pacman -S fcitx5-pinyin-zhwiki<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置环境变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># /etc/profile</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># ～/.xprofile</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> GTK_IM_MODULE=输入法名<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> XMODIFIERS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@im=输入法名&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> QT_IM_MODULE=输入法名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置fcitx5 material主题</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># ~/.config/fcitx5/conf/classicui.conf</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 垂直候选列表</span><br>Vertical Candidate List=False<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 按屏幕 DPI 使用</span><br>PerScreenDPI=True<br><span class="hljs-comment"># Font (设置成你喜欢的字体)</span><br>Font=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI 14&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 主题</span><br>Theme=Material-Color-Black<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>字体</p><p>将Windows下的字体文件放到一个文件夹中，然后放入注释的目录中，切换到新的文件夹后，执行命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># /usr/share/local/fonts/*</span><br>mkfontscale<br>mkfontdir<br>fc-cache -fv<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
